list.name: Default Changelist
list.comment: Pause menu's quit button now returns to the main menu as intended. ChangeTheme method now works correctly. The bug where the KeyHandler and AnimationTimers of GamePanel were active after returning to MainMenuPanel is fixed. This used to allow the user to open PauseMenuPanel from the MainMenuPanel.

task.summary: created ScreenManager and MainMenuPanel classes. MainMenuPanel now has a background image, a title, and buttons.
Changed MainMenuPanel style and fonts. Added MainMenuPanel exit on click function. Created Ship class and added an Image for it. GamePanel now has a Ship Image at the center.
The Ship can shoot now. The bullet moves smoothly and in either direction. GameCharacter class is created and inheritance relationship between it and Ship and Bullet classes is established.
fixed the enemy visibility issues on minimap
bullet sound effect is added (when user presses space)
